{"id":8839,"date":"2021-03-03T12:03:42","date_gmt":"2021-03-03T06:33:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=8839"},"modified":"2021-03-10T14:31:30","modified_gmt":"2021-03-10T09:01:30","slug":"why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.html","title":{"rendered":"Why Hire AngularJS Developers for Application Development"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8840\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.jpg\" alt=\"Hire AngularJS Developers for Application Development \" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development-768x373.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>AngularJS is a powerful JavaScript Framework allowing extending HTML vocabulary for your application maintained by Google and by a group of individuals and corporations to oversee challenges in developing single-page applications that are expressive, readable, and fast to develop. Fully extensible and compatible with other libraries, AngularJS provides a comprehensive toolset to develop your application.<\/p>\n<p>Easy to customize, this toolset allows the replacement of every feature based on unique development workflow and feature needs. It is important to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-angular-js-developer.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hire AngularJS developers<\/a> for Application Development to leverage the latest features.<\/p>\n<p>AngularJS provides an extension of HTML vocabulary for your application. While HTML is great for declaring static documents, it does not work while declaring dynamic views in web-applications. The result of the environment is extraordinarily expressive, readable, and quick to develop.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Key_Features_of_AngularJS\"><\/span>Key Features of AngularJS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Data_Binding_Automatic_way_to\"><\/span>Data Binding: Automatic way to<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Update the view when the model changes<\/li>\n<li>Update the model whenever the view changes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>It removes the hassles of DOM manipulation from the list of things you have to worry about.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controller\"><\/span>Controller<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Controllers are the behavior driving the DOM elements. AngularJS allows expressing the action in a clean, readable form and eliminates the boilerplate of DOM update, callback registration, or watching model changes.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Plain_JavaScript\"><\/span>Plain JavaScript<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>With AngularJS, there is no need to inherit from proprietary types to wrap the model in accessors methods. AngularJS models are JavaScript objects making code easy to test, maintain, reuse, and free from boilerplate.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_Hire_AngularJS_developers_for_Application_Development\"><\/span>Why Hire AngularJS developers for Application Development?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Build_High-Performance_Applications\"><\/span>Build High-Performance Applications<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>AngularJS helps in creating fully-functional and feature-rich web applications for its quick development.<a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/angularjs-web-development-tools-features-and-benefits.html\"> Key features of AngularJS<\/a> that allow high-performance building applications in a short turnaround time include:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Routing<\/li>\n<li>Form validation<\/li>\n<li>Data binding<\/li>\n<li>Directives<\/li>\n<li>Filters<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>There are several other aspects like CLI (Common Line Interface) and IDEs, making this framework high in performance when it comes to app development.<\/p>\n<p>The IDEs of AngularJS is better than any other JS framework, and it helps professional developers track down mistakes instantly. And with the CLI, it becomes simpler for developers to make web apps and attach elements quickly, which leads to rapid web app development.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Engaging_UI_Lightweight_Apps\"><\/span>Engaging UI &amp; Lightweight Apps<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>If you are looking to build lightweight apps, AngularJS provides easy-to-customize elements that allow AngularJS developers to design the UI based on the client\u2019s requirements. Several factors such as market status, target audience, and app type make the UI engaging.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Integration_of_MVC_and_MVVM_Architecture\"><\/span>Integration of MVC and MVVM Architecture<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>AngularJS utilizes MVC architecture to split frameworks into MVC architecture, allowing developers to save time, fulfill deadlines quickly, and meet the project delivery schedule. Aside from this, MVVM and MVC applications are easy to apply.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Seamless_Testing\"><\/span>Seamless Testing<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Designed to be testable, AngularJS comes pre-bundled with mocks &amp; encourages behavior-view separation to leverage dependency injection. It also comes with an end-to-end scenario runner to eliminate test flakiness by understanding the inner workings of AngularJS.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Power_of_Localization\"><\/span>Power of Localization<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>One critical factor of the app is localization. AngularJS&#8217;s locale aware filters and stemming directives provide AngularJS developers with building blocks to make applications available in different locales.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Code_Reusability\"><\/span>Code Reusability<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>This is one of the top features of AngularJS, code reusability. This feature allows developers to reuse the code that is already written seamlessly. As a result, developers save a lot of resources in terms of time. Hence, there is a chance to deliver a mobile app development project earlier and get delivered on a relevant timeline.<\/p>\n<p>Its reusability of code helps to make modifications in the apps quickly. In most cases, few tweaks in the code update can upgrade your web app with the latest improvements and features. Alternatively, you can hire expert AngularJS developers to assure project delivery as early as possible.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Two-Way_Data_Binding\"><\/span>Two-Way Data Binding<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Two-way binding makes it simple for developers to create the app interface. Any changes made to the UI of the app are depicted in the app interface automatically and vice versa.<\/p>\n<p>Developers save a lot of time with this feature as the platform&#8217;s two-way data binding allows in-depth analysis of modifications made to the UI directly in the app interface. This key feature makes AngularJS one of the top frameworks for web application development in the present digital era.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Reusable_Components\"><\/span>Reusable Components<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>We use directives to create reusable components to hide complex DOM structure, CSS, and behavior, focusing on what the application does or how it looks separately.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.html\/#Key_Features_of_AngularJS\" title=\"Key Features of AngularJS\">Key Features of AngularJS<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.html\/#Data_Binding_Automatic_way_to\" title=\"Data Binding: Automatic way to\">Data Binding: Automatic way to<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.html\/#Controller\" title=\"Controller\">Controller<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-for-application-development.html\/#Plain_JavaScript\" title=\"Plain JavaScript\">Plain JavaScript<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/why-hire-angularjs-developers-